## 0.1 Preface

Using [Erc271 tokens](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-721) from public blockchain Ethereum contract [`0xBC4CA0EdA7647A8aB7C2061c2E118A18a936f13D`](https://etherscan.io/address/0xBC4CA0EdA7647A8aB7C2061c2E118A18a936f13D) advance computer vision algorithm describes (*reviews*) each token with sequential <img style="pointer-events: none" src="nft.png"/>**DOWNLOAD**<img style="pointer-events: none" src="nft.png"/> using [x.org](https://x.org) X11 color names training data set `rgb.txt` with Linux OS `sed` based technologies for novel length content generation.

Proprietary WORDs are contained in `phrases.txt`, `apes.txt`, `is.txt`, `bored.txt`, `with.txt`, `on.txt`, `with.txt`, `ground.txt`, `being.txt`.

## 4.2 Code Source
```bash
#!/bin/bash

contract=BC4CA0EdA7647A8aB7C2061c2E118A18a936f13D

gw=https://ipfs.io/ipfs/
scan="https://etherscan.io/readContract?m=normal&a=0x${contract}&v=0x${contract}"
rootdir=$(curl -s $scan | egrep -ao "ipfs:..[^/]*")

for i in {0..9999}; do
  nft=$(curl -s $gw${rootdir:7}/$i | egrep -ao "ipfs:..\w*")
  color=$(curl -s $gw${nft:7} |
    egrep "^\s*$(convert - -alpha off -depth 8 txt:- |
    fgrep -m1 '70,0:' |
    sed 's/^.*srgb.\([0-9,]*\).$/ \1,/;s/[0-9]\{2\},/\\w\\w,/g;s/ //g;s/,/\\s+/g')" rgb.txt |
    head | shuf -n1 |
    cut -f3,4 |
    head -n1 |
    sed 's/ /-/g;s/[0-9X]//g;s/\([A-Z]\)/\L\1/;s/\([A-Z]\)/-\L\1/g')
  out=$(shuf -n1 phrases.txt |
    sed "s/APE/$(shuf -n1 apes.txt)/;
         s/IS/$(shuf -n1 is.txt)/;
         s/BORED/$(shuf -n1 bored.txt)/;
         s/ON/$(shuf -n1 on.txt)/;
         s/WITH/$(shuf -n1 with.txt)/;
         s/GROUND/$(shuf -n1 ground.txt)/;
         s/BEING/$(shuf -n1 being.txt)/
         s/COLOR/$color/")
  echo "<span style=\"color:${color//-}\" title=\"$nft\">${out^}</span>"
done
```
